389	**Guild override — kit instructions not loaded when guild overrides:**
390	Same setup as above but kit role has `instructionsFile: './role.md'`. Verify the file is never read (no fs access for the overridden kit role).
391	
392	**Permission scoping — valid permissions kept:**
