397	
398	**Permission scoping — wildcard prefix blocked:**
399	Kit contributes a role with permission `['*:*']`. The permission is dropped with a warning. Kit contributes `['*:read']`. Also dropped.
400	
401	**Permission scoping — malformed permission (no colon) dropped:**
402	Kit contributes a role with permission `['nocolon']`. Dropped with a warning.
403	
404	**Malformed roles field — non-object skipped silently:**
405	Kit has `roles: 'not-an-object'`. No crash, no roles registered.
406	
407	**Malformed role entry — missing permissions warned:**
408	Kit has `roles: { bad: { strict: true } }`. Warning emitted, `bad` not registered.
409	
410	**Malformed role entry — non-object value skipped silently:**
